message.content: cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DL. The paper describes a graph database for exploring and investigating scientific literature, which involves elements of database management (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data mining (cs.SI) to extract insights from the literature. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of citation-based metrics, which could fall under the category of deep learning (cs.DL) if machine learning techniques are used to analyze citation patterns.
